d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rssgmatt/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rssgmatt</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 8, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This was a great purchase, I look forward to seeing the progress of the app as the social media grows.\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Pleased to find a solution...</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/designwise/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2947e6d86e2c3c6af628b6ce21085d55?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2947e6d86e2c3c6af628b6ce21085d55?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/designwise/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">designwise</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 2, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It works and has a variety of features above and beyond Facebook. I will use it from now on. Thanks!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Free version works fine too</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/halucska/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2c339b46a476576b4ca5c07661345769?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2c339b46a476576b4ca5c07661345769?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/halucska/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">halucska</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 2, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I found only a small bug: accents break the hashtag labels.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">No support for the premium version and account deactivated</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dchristof/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b3d82fc7730870d7200a3338b0549e01?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b3d82fc7730870d7200a3338b0549e01?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dchristof/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Daphne C. <small>(dchristof)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 24, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I have recently bought the EasySocialFeed premium plugin and had a problem with load more not working. I opened up a support ticket and after the first reply from Danish Ali Malik I never got another reply to my emails and problem still remains. So I have actually paid for a plugin which is not working. I sent several emails which remain unanswered and when I try to login to my account in easysocialfeed.com I can\'t, although it was working a few weeks back. I can\'t even restore my password because I get the error that my email does not exist which means my account was deleted. I\'m leaving this bad review here to make sure I get noticed since the plugin developers don\'t reply to any of my emails or messages and to prevent others from buying this plugin.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anjan86/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b389d2bf63832d33452ae2966a2ea1b1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b389d2bf63832d33452ae2966a2ea1b1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anjan86/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">anjan86</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 12, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">good</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very useful!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/crispybran/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3f0b5ac6ace04e7c4ea161f999e69c8c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3f0b5ac6ace04e7c4ea161f999e69c8c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/crispybran/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">crispybran</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 27, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I appreciate this plugin very much.  Others cripple the software in it\'s basic usage.  This is a great plugin for our basic needs.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy to use and responsive help from the developer</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cowanservices/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/409622d14939adf70a8c641f720855b7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/409622d14939adf70a8c641f720855b7?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cowanservices/\" class=\"reviewer-name\"> <small>(cowanservices)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 27, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I initially tried to use this plugin, but there was a functionality missing that I had to have so I decided to try another one. After I disabled it, the developer reached out to ask why I wasn\'t using it. I explained, and he adapted the plugin to work for my use case. I\'m impressed! My pre-sales question wasn\'t answered which was a little annoying, but other than that, I\'m happy.\n\nLisa</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy to use and it works</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pessimisticoptimist/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/67d6bcd9e60f0f2202f9f5bee0b95ada?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/67d6bcd9e60f0f2202f9f5bee0b95ada?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pessimisticoptimist/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">PessimisticOptimist</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 20, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Easy to set up, excellent shortcode generator to pick display options.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Did not work at all</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"